               <msContents>
                  <summary>Asmat prayer against evil eye and other evil spirits, (accordion-fold book)</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="3v" to="12r" facs="004">Fols 3v–12r</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer against evil eye and other evil spirits</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                       በስመ፡ አብ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ዓይነ፡ ጥላ፡ ገርጋሪያ፡ ዓይነ፡ ባርያ፡ ወሌጌዎን፡ ዓይነ፡ ጥላ፡ ወጥላወጊ፡ ዓይነ፡ መቀኛ፡ ወዓይነ፡ ትንኰለኛ፡ መጋኛ፡ ወጉሥምት፡ ፌራ፡ ወንዳድ፡</incipit>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
